# Minimal Diffs Rule

## Intent
Keep agent edits small, targeted, and safe.

## Requirements
- Use minimal patches only. Change the smallest region required.
- Never rewrite an entire file for a localized change.
- If a file is over 800 lines, refactor it into smaller components/hooks before feature edits.
- Extract repeated blocks instead of duplicating code.
- Avoid formatting-only changes unless explicitly requested.
- Do not touch unrelated files.

## Verification
- After edits, run relevant lint/typecheck/tests for the changed scope.
